<div class="footer-cta card text-center">
  <h2>Start with a workflow your agent can follow.</h2>
  <p>Install AIOS, create or adopt a project, then give Codex explicit docs, skills, tasks, and review criteria.</p>
  <div class="actions">
    <a href="/getting-started" class="btn btn-primary">Read Documentation</a>
    <a href="/guides/workflow" class="btn btn-secondary">View Workflow</a>
    <code>npm install -g @donihadimas/aios</code>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .card {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-card-start), var(--color-card-end));
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    margin: 4rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .btn {
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
  }
  .btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }
  .btn:focus-visible {
    outline: 3px solid var(--color-focus);
    outline-offset: 3px;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-accent-contrast);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent-hover);
    color: var(--color-accent-contrast);
  }
  .btn-secondary {
    color: var(--color-text);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--color-badge-bg);
  }
  code {
    max-width: 100%;
    background: var(--color-code-bg);
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono", monospace;
    color: var(--color-accent-2);
    overflow-wrap: anywhere;
  }
</style>
